title: Jenna Dewan Tatum wants more kids
text: Jenna Dewan Tatum wants more kids Monday, 26 October 2015 (20 minutes ago) The 34-year-old actress, who has two-year-old daughter Everly with husband Channing Tatum, admits she is keen to expand their family but doesn’t know when it will be the right time, reported In Touch Weekly. (Source: Reuters) Actress Jenna Dewan Tatum says she definitely would like another baby. The 34-year-old actress, who has two-year-old daughter Everly with husband Channing Tatum, admits she is keen to expand their family but doesn’t know when it will be the right time, reported In Touch Weekly. “We definitely want another baby. We’re just not sure when! I love our daughter so much. She’s literally the light of my life,’ the actress said. …read more Source:: Indian Express…
